  'Resource', 'Problem Set', 'NMTC',
  2026, 'Problem Set 1', 'Problem 3: Angle Chasing (a) In acute△ABCwith incenterI, prove that ̸ BIC= 90 ◦ + 1 2 ̸ BAC (b) In acute△ABCwith incenterI. LetMbe the midpoint of the arc BCnot containingA. Show thatMis the circumcenter of△BIC (c) In acute triangle ̸ ABC, letI A be the reflection of the incenterIover M(Defined as in the previous problem). Show thatBI A andCI B are the external angle-bisector of ̸ ABCand ̸ ACBrespectively. (d) In acute△ABC, DefineI B andI C similarly to howI A was defined earlier. Show thatIis the orthocenter of△I AIBIC (*) Page 4 NMTC Problem Set 1Introduction15th February 2026',
