  29, '29', 'Physics',
  'Physics MCQ', 'Subject MCQ', 'MCQ',
  'Part II', 'Physics MCQs', 'NSTC',
  2022, 'NSTC 2022 Physics Paper', 'A 1.0-kilogram rubber ball traveling east at 4.0 meters per second hits a wall and bounces back toward the west at 2.0 meters per second. Compared to the kinetic energy of the ball before it hits the wall, the kinetic energy of the ball after it bounces off the wall is',
  '["one-fourth as great","the same","one-half as great","four times as great"]'::jsonb, 0, 'Finding: Kinitial = 1 2(1)(4)2 = 8 Joule Kfinial = 1 2(1)(2)2 = 2 Joule Thus, Kf Ki = 2 Kf = 1 4Ki',
  5, '', '{}'::jsonb
),
